text:
Hi @gedrgesfsdfwe4046, we eat a lot of leftovers from Mija, but that being said. We are open four days a week and have a set menu which is prepaid for the same reason to minimize food waste. Everyday when prepping at Mija we know exactly the amounts since everything is weighed out and portioned. When Tina mentioned, around 6 months ago, that we were eating a lot of leftovers we were still working on prepping accurate amounts, and back then we were literally 4 people total including Tina, now we have a bigger team that all bring food home. 
And this video is shoot over one day by 3 people that all share all the food that we shoot. No food was wasted, some was brought home for later snacks and meals. 
Have a good day! 
Kevin K
